    <div class="row gx-3">
        <div class="col- col-sm-6 col-md-5">

            <div @click="_testBtn('suicidal')" class="mobile-btn suicidal">I feel suicidal</div>
            <div @click="_testBtn('depressed')" class="mobile-btn depressed">I feel depressed</div>
            <div @click="_testBtn('stuck')" class="mobile-btn stuck">I feel stuck</div>
            <div @click="_testBtn('just-talk')" class="mobile-btn just-talk">I just want to talk to someone
            </div>
            <div @click="_testBtn('professional')" class="mobile-btn professional">I want to talk to a
                professional</div>

        </div>
        <div class="col- col-sm-6 col-md-7">
            <div class="h-100 p-3 text-white bg-dark-blue rounded-3">
                <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">What is <b>Rafiki?</b></h1>
                <p class="col-md-12">
                    <b>Rafiki</b> is Swahili for <b><i>friend.</i></b> </p>
                <p class="col-md-12">
                    Rafiki is the place you go when you need a friend to talk to.</p>

                <p class="col-md-12">
                    We accord you a safe, self
                    sharing space where you can
                    unravel yourself and reconnect
                    with your true self.
                </p>
                <p class="col-md-12">
                    At <b>Rafiki</b>, you have a friend that hears you,
                    understands you and what you are going
                    through and is available to offer you
                    counsel at the touch of a dial in the comfort
                    of your home wherever you are. </p>
                <p class="col-md-12">
                    No matter what you are going through,
                    <b>Rafiki</b> assures you of the support you need
                    without prejudice and utmost confidentiality in a
                    loving environment that wants to see you reconnect
                    and realign with your true self as you fulfil your
                    divine purpose.
                </p>

                <p class="col-md-12">
                    <b>Rafiki</b> is a platform created by a
                    group of friends consisting of mental health
                    practitioners, well-wishers, and community leaders
                    who have come together to offer mental health first aid.
                </p>

                <p class="col-md-12">
                    <b>Rafiki</b> has a directory of professionals ready to
                    attend to individuals needing mental health first aid.
                </p>

                <div @click="_testBtn('register-professional')" class="mobile-btn professional">I'm a
                    professional, onboard me!</div>

            </div>
        </div>
